  "texts": [
    "The buffer directly saves each interaction in the chat history.",
    "ConversationBufferWin-dowMemory applies a window to memory.",
    "EmoRoBERTA modelIn our Chatbot, we added, in a novel way, the emotional component through the use of the EmoRoBERTA algorithm [42].",
    "EmoRoBERTa is a cutting-edge model designed for emotion detection in NLP, advancing the understanding of emotions in human communication.",
    "Developed using the RoBERTa framework by Facebook, it leverages pretraining and refinement on a large dataset, notably the extensive GoEmotions dataset."
